snippet.title: Tour de France 2024 🚴‍♂️ Launch trailer
snippet.description:
The official game of the Tour de France 2024 is available now! #tdf2024  💛

Discover the new multiplayer mode, new team additions, new rules customization, dirt roads and play real teams as Pro Leader and Pro Team 🤩

Available on PC, PS4, PS5 and Xbox X|S.
